data.description: Spacious 4 bed 2 bath home in China Spring ISD! Enter the beautiful living room with durable tile floors that lead through to the kitchen. The kitchen features beautiful dark granite counter tops and black appliances- plenty of storage and a generous dining area. The owner bought the home with the garage already converted to a large living area/gameroom/bar/movie viewing room or whatever you use suits your family. The master bedroom is large and connected to the master bath which has separate shower and bathtub plus a his and hers closet. The other 3 bedrooms have lots of space and share the hallway bathroom. Lots of space in the backyard with an extended patio slab and a gazebo perfect for entertaining. Won't last long!
